<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.png">
    <title>janderf_dev</title>

    <style>
        /* ===== RESET E FONTES ===== */
        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 20s ease infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% {background-position:0% 50%;}
            50% {background-position:100% 50%;}
            100% {background-position:0% 50%;}
        }

        /* ===== CONTAINER ===== */
        .container {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* ===== LOGO ===== */
        .logo {
            width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s forwards;
        }

        /* ===== TÍTULO ===== */
        h1 {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,198,255,0.5);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s forwards;
        }

        p.description {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ccc;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s forwards;
            animation-delay: 1s;
        }

        /* ===== TIMELINE ===== */
        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px;
            left: 5%;
            width: 90%;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(0,198,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 2px;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .point {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0,198,255,0.2);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px #00c6ff);
            animation: bounce 2s infinite alternate;
            transition: transform 0.3s, filter 0.3s;
        }
        .point:hover {
            transform: scale(1.4);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px #00c6ff);
        }
        .point-text {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            max-width: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* ===== CARDS ESTILO APPLE ===== */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 320px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeUp 1s forwards;
        }
        .card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1s; }
        .card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
        .card h3 {
            color: #00c6ff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .card p {
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* ===== BOTÃO ===== */
        .btn {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #00c6ff;
            color: #111;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #00a2cc;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,198,255,0.4);
        }

        /* ===== ANIMAÇÕES ===== */
        @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }
        @keyframes bounce { from { transform: translateY(0px); } to { transform: translateY(-15px); } }
        @keyframes fadeUp { to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">

        <!-- TÍTULO E DESCRIÇÃO -->
        <h1>Início</h1>
        <p class="description">
            Guia completo para me tornar um dos melhores programadores de TI, explorar novas culturas e conquistar experiências incríveis pelo mundo.

        <!-- TIMELINE DIVERTIDA -->
        <div class="timeline">
            <div>
                <div class="point">🏁</div>
                <div class="point-text">Largada</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="point">📊</div>
                <div class="point-text">Planejar</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="point">🎯</div>
                <div class="point-text">Objetivo</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="point">📚</div>
                <div class="point-text">Estudos</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="point">🏆</div>
                <div class="point-text">Conquista</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CARDS DE PROJETOS -->
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Projetos</h3>
            <p>Mostra os sites, apps ou jogos que criei. Cada projeto com título, descrição e link para ver funcionando.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Skills & Habilidades</h3>
            <p>HTML, CSS, JavaScript, VS Code, GitHub e design. Cada card mostra o que sei e minhas ferramentas favoritas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Conteúdo Educativo</h3>
            <p>Dicas e tutoriais rápidos, como criar favicon perfeito ou usar GitHub Pages.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- BOTÃO VOLTAR -->
        <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.href='index.html'">Voltar</button>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
